Hello everyone,
Here is my post because since July 1st I had a bad trip on LSD,
I need to say that before this bad trip I was hitting 20 pills a day and I was doing some 1 week every two months with heavy doses (Taz, coke, LSD, and everything else)...For 3 years,
now I am going to tell you how it passed.
Have a good week, I'm waiting for you
On Friday night everyone is doing well
We consumed 5 grams of speed plus all the MD.
Saturday morning after a sleepless night I'm going to work just the morning from 9 am to 12 pm in the afternoon,
We didn't continue.
I continued on my side to shoot bullets and to type speed.
a coworker is holding the glass with a drop of the LSD vial
I hesitated at first then after I told myself come on I'll take it (something I shouldn't have done).
The evening continues normally and the two other so-called colleagues had decided to make us drink a lot super colleagues.....
On this famous beach there were a lot of people and one of the two colleagues told us there's someone looking for trouble we're going to fight....
I think the product should go down because I wouldn't be able to fight like that
so because of that I forced myself to resist the product
The paranoia is starting to engulf me, everyone is making a scene
The two other colleagues who hadn't taken anything, started looking for the guys who are mad at us
I being totally crazy I said to myself it's going to go away at some point
Time passes, nothing happens.
brief we leave the beach and then we go to my place
I ask them if the guys are following us.
He does not respond.
We arrive at my place and then he leaves me all alone at my place with my girlfriend who was sleeping...
I continue my bad all night
Impossible to sleep, I'm thinking and at the slightest noise I go out with a bat....
The day rises and I begin to fall asleep because I had just realized that there was nothing
The night passes normally,
I wake up and I am still under the effect of LSD and the rest
I told myself it's normal
So we were on Sunday and the next day I had to work.
The day is passing normally
I shoot some bullets then I nap,
Sunday passes and Monday arrives
I still feel like shit.
I still think this is normal with the box I got....
So at 2 PM I was supposed to take the job
Right now I'm eating a little and I'm taking a big line of speed to have energy at work...
so I take the car and I go to work
Arrive at work, as soon as I open the store I start to feel dizzy, my heart starts beating at 200 and I feel like I'm going to faint.
Reassuring me, I'm going to buy some Snickers bars and something to drink.
After that I go back to work and another crisis...
Panicked I called my mother.. because the colleagues were not there....
after that his mother took me to the doctor
He asks me what I did and I spill all my bag
and my mother took it rather well finally she knows that I was shady..
The Doctor told me to wait for the product to go down, it will take a few months then that's it.
I told him I had vision problems
I told him I had vision problems
He told me it was normal too and that it would go back down.
For my anxiety attacks he prescribed me lizanxia an anti-anxiety medication finally against anxiety
I take 1 in the morning 1 in the evening,
It calms me but the voices in my head don't stop.
It often gives me a good headache...
Following this bad experience, I stopped everything, no more bullets, nothing.
My girlfriend doesn't understand what's happening to me and doesn't care much.
I fired him.
My colleagues also don't care either so I fired him too.
At the same time I moved.
I currently live with my mother, but I found an apartment
but I cannot live there because I have anxiety attacks.
In addition to that I have tons of thoughts in my head
Currently it's been 5 months today that I did this bad and at the level of my sight I still look behind a mirror
Finally these troubles are especially bad when it's sunny...
The voices in my head don't stop from morning until night...
My thoughts are confused from always doing the same thing
I have the impression of living the same day every day.
I always have my work, I no longer have any friends except 2 cousins and my brother who are far from me.
